Terminals which are not used

   COMMA


Grammar

    0 $accept: Prog $end

    1 Prog: StmtList

    2 StmtList: Stmt StmtList
    3         | /* empty */

    4 Stmt: Decl
    5     | Asgn
    6     | IfStmt
    7     | WhlStmt
    8     | PrntStmt
    9     | Blk

   10 Blk: LC StmtList RC

   11 Decl: Typ ID SEMI

   12 Typ: INT
   13    | FLOAT

   14 Asgn: ID ASGN Expr SEMI

   15 PrntStmt: PRINT LP ID RP SEMI

   16 IfStmt: IF LP Expr RP Blk
   17       | IF LP Expr RP Blk ELSE Blk

   18 WhlStmt: WHILE LP Expr RP Blk

   19 Expr: Expr OR Expr
   20     | Expr AND Expr
   21     | Expr EQ Expr
   22     | Expr NEQ Expr
   23     | Expr LT Expr
   24     | Expr GT Expr
   25     | Expr LEQ Expr
   26     | Expr GEQ Expr
   27     | Expr PLUS Expr
   28     | Expr MINUS Expr
   29     | Expr MUL Expr
   30     | Expr DIV Expr
   31     | Expr MOD Expr
   32     | NOT LP Expr RP
   33     | LP Expr RP
   34     | ID
   35     | ICON
   36     | FCON


